Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.24,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:20.31,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0\rop-cn\blur2}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:33.98,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何れ程　歩いたろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:37.94,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足の痛みだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.03,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}その距離を物語る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:48.12,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}長い夜を越えた絶景への期待が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:51.14,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日　僕を生かしている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:57.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神々の霊峰　新緑の宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:02.26,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟の最奥　蒼穹の涯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:08.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏破してみせる　限界は無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惑星の隅々まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.02,op-jp,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.27,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0\pos(640,-2)\rop-cn\blur2}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:22.07,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能の闇を祓って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.07,0:23:27.66,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神話を日常に変えていく{\fsp0\rop-cn\blur2}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:36.87,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一歩ずつ石を穿つ様な　この歩みで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:41.79,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世界を拡げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.24,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:20.31,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:33.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我腳步不停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:37.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有雙腳的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知曉走過的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:48.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我期待著漫漫長夜後的絕美風景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:51.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:57.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神之靈峰 新綠宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:02.26,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟深處 蒼穹盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:08.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要一一到達 永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要走遍每一個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.02,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.27,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:22.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驅散名為不可能的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.07,0:23:27.66,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}將神話變為日常的{\fsp0}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:36.87,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一步又一步 如滴水穿石般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:41.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拓寬眼前的世界
